source: Adds support for advanced attributes on images like a copyright attribute.
The copyright attribute is used as a tooltip when the mouse hovers over the image.
The copyright will only be shown when it has been supplied
The file id that the attribute belongs to.
The name of the Image attribute entity.
The time that the entity was created.
The time that the entity was last edited.
This field stores the ID of an image file as an integer value.
Uses data-* attributes on <img> tags to add advanced functionalities to images.
